{"tid":1163112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本港失業率維持2.8%","createTime":"2019-05-20T09:05:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T09:51:54.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a0911e6c0b22dedf0802ae0d2b0c2a4e982a3775","tid":1163112,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:05:43.000Z","msg":"統計處公布，本港2月至4月經季節調整失業率為2.8%，與1月至3月數字相同，就業不足率維持1%。<br />\n<br />\n總就業人數由1月至3月的3,860,400人，上升到2月至4月的3,865,000人，增加約4600人，同期總勞動人口由3,970,800人，上升至3,977,300人，增加約6500人；失業人數（不經季節調整）由1月至3月的110,400人，上升至2月至4月的112,300人，增加約1900人，同期的就業不足人數由38,900人下跌至38,000人，減少約900人。<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局長羅致光表示：勞工市場短期內料會維持大致穩定，惟外圍環境仍具挑戰，政府會密切留意本地勞工市場發展。"},{"pid":"f1a428f36f2a09a25acb0a5c2a5c8028c357eac4","tid":1163112,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:06:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190520/s00001/1558342091071/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190520%2Fs00001%2F1558342091071%2F&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=a0dcae03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190520%2Fs00001%2F1558342091071%2F&h=0e7e12eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190520/s00001/1558342091071/</a>"},{"pid":"2c2308bb2b6c18b77a81ac3d148d41815068c988","tid":1163112,"uid":193436,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:07:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c116aa7e8934227cf2bcc1984cfe621beff309cb","tid":1163112,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T09:19:08.000Z","msg":"死咗上去大灣區「發展」就唔當係失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2353d689a901d5c12b69a